Class OverdeterminationValidator

java.lang.Object
  org.sbml.jsbml.validator.OverdeterminationValidator

public class OverdeterminationValidator
extends Object

This class creates a bipartite graph and a matching for the given model using the algorithm by Hopcroft and Karp (1973).
